   "source": [
    "# VibeThinker-3B Inference (Colab)\n",
    "\n",
    "Run VibeThinker-3B — a 3-billion-parameter dense reasoning model by WeiboAI —\n",
    "directly in Google Colab.\n",
    "\n",
    "[![Open In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)]"
    "(https://colab.research.google.com/github/OMCHOKSI108/VibeThinkerModel/blob/main/notebooks/VibeThinker_3B_Inference_Colab.ipynb)\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "**Attribution**\n",
    "\n",
    "| Resource | Link |\n",
    "|----------|------|\n",
    "| Original Model | [WeiboAI/VibeThinker-3B](https://huggingface.co/WeiboAI/VibeThinker-3B) |\n",
    "| Original GitHub | [WeiboAI/VibeThinker](https://github.com/WeiboAI/VibeThinker) |\n",
    "| This Mirror | [OMCHOKSI108/VibeThinker-3B](https://huggingface.co/OMCHOKSI108/VibeThinker-3B) |\n",
    "| Technical Report | [arXiv:2606.16140](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.16140) |\n",
    "\n",
    "Model and code credits belong to **WeiboAI and contributors**.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Run this notebook in a Colab GPU runtime:**\n",
    "> `Runtime` → `Change runtime type` → `T4 GPU` or `A100`.\n",
    "> The model requires ~8 GB VRAM in bfloat16. A T4 GPU (16 GB) is sufficient."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "setup"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 1. Runtime Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "Check that a GPU is available."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "gpu_check"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "\n",
    "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "    print(f\"GPU: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"VRAM: {torch.cuda.get_device_properties(0).total_memory / 1e9:.1f} GB\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"No GPU detected. Switch to a GPU runtime: Runtime > Change runtime type > T4 GPU\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "deps"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 2. Install Dependencies\n",
    "\n",
    "Install the required Python packages."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "install"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
