  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "optimization"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 7. Memory Optimization Notes\n",
    "\n",
    "VibeThinker-3B is ~6 GB in bfloat16. Here are ways to reduce memory usage:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Technique | VRAM Saved | Notes |\n",
    "|-----------|-----------|-------|\n",
    "| `torch.float16` instead of `bfloat16` | ~0 GB | Same memory; slightly different numerics |\n",
    "| `device_map=\"auto\"` | — | Offloads layers to CPU if GPU is full |\n",
    "| 4-bit quantization (bitsandbytes) | ~4.5 GB | Use `load_in_4bit=True` |\n",
    "| 8-bit quantization (bitsandbytes) | ~3 GB | Use `load_in_8bit=True` |\n",
    "| Reduce `max_new_tokens` | — | Shorter outputs use less memory |\n",
    "\n",
    "**Example — 4-bit loading:**\n",
    "```python\n",
    "model = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(\n",
    "    MODEL_NAME,\n",
    "    load_in_4bit=True,\n",
    "    device_map=\"auto\",\n",
    ")\n",
    "```\n",
    "Note: 4-bit quantization may affect output quality."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "troubleshooting"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 8. Troubleshooting\n",
    "\n",
    "| Problem | Solution |\n",
    "|---------|----------|\n",
    "| Out of memory (CUDA OOM) | Use 4-bit quantization or reduce `max_new_tokens` |\n",
    "| Model download fails | Check internet connection; try the original `WeiboAI/VibeThinker-3B` repo |\n",
    "| `transformers` version error | Ensure `transformers>=4.54.0` is installed |\n",
    "| Slow inference | Use a T4 or A100 GPU runtime; reduce `max_new_tokens` |\n",
    "| Runtime disconnects | Colab free tier may disconnect after prolonged use; save intermediate results |\n",
    "| Tokenizer error | Add `trust_remote_code=True` when loading tokenizer |"
   ]
  },
